# Folder Structure Conventions

## General Rules
Inside the `src` folder, the project must follow this structure:

```
src/
    app/          # Routes, pages, and Next.js app directory files
    components/   # Reusable UI components
    hooks/        # Reusable hooks
    lib/          # Utility functions etc
    types/        # Shared type definitions (type aliases preferred)
    constants.ts  # Shared constants
```

## Examples

**Correct**
```
src/components/user-card.tsx
src/hooks/use-user-data.ts
src/hooks/use-fetch-data.ts
src/constants.ts
```

## File Matching
- Apply this folder structure to all new files and directories inside `src/`.
- Enforce kebab-case for all files and folder names.
